---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Advanced Treatments – Bliss Dermacare" description="Medical-grade aesthetic procedures at Bliss Dermacare: PRP, Lip Filler, Erectile Dysfunction Injectables, Collagen Induction Therapy, and GLP-1 Weight Loss Program in Pebble Creek, FL.">

  <section class="py-14 bg-[#faf9f7] border-b border-neutral-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-4">
        <a href="/services/" class="hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">All Services</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <span class="text-neutral-900 font-medium">Advanced Treatments</span>
      </div>
      <span class="text-primary-600 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xs font-semibold mb-4 block">Clinical Aesthetics</span>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-4">Advanced Treatments</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 max-w-xl mx-auto">Medical-grade aesthetic procedures for transformative, lasting results. All advanced services require a standalone booking. Consultation required for select treatments.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-14 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-primary-100 hover:border-primary-300">
          <div class="relative h-52 overflow-hidden"><img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3738338/pexels-photo-3738338.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600" alt="PRP platelet-rich plasma blood draw and injection therapy" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" /><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"></div></div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-2">PRP (Platelet-Rich Plasma)</h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mb-4">Harness your body's own growth factors to rejuvenate skin, stimulate collagen, and accelerate healing. Ideal for face, neck, scalp, and hair restoration.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-sm text-neutral-600 mb-5">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Natural collagen &amp; tissue regeneration</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Effective for skin, scalp &amp; hair restoration</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Standalone booking required</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between"><div><p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">$399</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">60 min / session</p></div><a href="/book/" data-service-id="prp-treatment" class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary-600 text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors">Book</a></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-primary-100 hover:border-primary-300">
          <div class="relative h-52 overflow-hidden"><img src="/images/lip-filler-treatment.jpg" alt="Lip filler hyaluronic acid injection cosmetic enhancement" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" /><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"></div></div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-2">Lip Filler</h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mb-4">Fuller, more defined lips with hyaluronic acid filler. Natural-looking enhancement with immediate results that last 6–12 months.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-sm text-neutral-600 mb-5">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Hyaluronic acid — reversible &amp; safe</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Immediate results, minimal downtime</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Lasts 6–12 months</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between"><div><p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">$599</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">45 min / syringe</p></div><a href="/book/" data-service-id="lip-filler" class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary-600 text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors">Book</a></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-primary-100 hover:border-primary-300">
          <div class="relative h-52 overflow-hidden"><img src="/images/ed-injectables-treatment.jpg" alt="Medical injectable treatment procedure" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" /><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"></div></div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-2">Erectile Dysfunction Injectables</h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mb-4">Clinically proven injectable therapy for ED. Discreet, professional treatment with noticeable improvement in performance and confidence.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-sm text-neutral-600 mb-5">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Clinically proven efficacy</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Discreet, professional environment</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Consultation included</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between"><div><p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">$499</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">60 min / session</p></div><a href="/book/" data-service-id="ed-injectables" class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary-600 text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors">Book</a></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-primary-100 hover:border-primary-300">
          <div class="relative h-52 overflow-hidden"><img src="/images/collagen-induction-therapy.jpg" alt="Collagen induction therapy — microneedling skin rejuvenation treatment" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" /><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"></div></div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-2">Collagen Induction Therapy</h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mb-4">Precision microneedling triggers your skin's natural collagen production. Reduces fine lines, scars, enlarged pores, and uneven texture over time.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-sm text-neutral-600 mb-5">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Targets fine lines, scars &amp; pores</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Stimulates natural collagen production</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Improves progressively over 3–6 sessions</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between"><div><p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">$299</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">60 min / session</p></div><a href="/book/" data-service-id="collagen-induction-therapy" class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary-600 text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors">Book</a></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-primary-100 hover:border-primary-300">
          <div class="relative h-52 overflow-hidden"><img src="/images/weight-loss-program.jpg" alt="Medical weight loss consultation and GLP-1 program" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" /><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"></div></div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-2">Weight Loss Program</h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mb-4">GLP-1 / Semiglutide-assisted medical weight loss with professional oversight. Personalized dosing, lifestyle guidance, and monthly monitoring for sustainable results.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-sm text-neutral-600 mb-5">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>GLP-1 / Semiglutide-assisted protocol</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Personalized dosing &amp; lifestyle plan</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Monthly monitoring included</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between"><div><p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">$299</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">/month · incl. consultation</p></div><a href="/book/" data-service-id="weight-loss-program" class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary-600 text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors">Book</a></div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-10 bg-neutral-50 border-t border-neutral-100">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-neutral-400 mb-4">Also Explore</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="/services/facials/" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-full text-sm text-neutral-700 hover:border-primary-300 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">Facials</a>
        <a href="/services/ancillary/" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-full text-sm text-neutral-700 hover:border-primary-300 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">Ancillary Services</a>
        <a href="/services/semipermanent-makeup/" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-full text-sm text-neutral-700 hover:border-primary-300 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">Semipermanent Makeup</a>
        <a href="/services/packages/" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-full text-sm text-neutral-700 hover:border-primary-300 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">Seasonal Packages</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-14 bg-neutral-900 text-white text-center">
    <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif mb-4">Ready to book?</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-400 mb-8">All advanced treatments are standalone bookings. We'll confirm your appointment within 24 hours.</p>
      <a href="/book/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-all font-medium shadow-lg">Request Booking <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"/></svg></a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
